<pb facs="1078966" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Viro <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimo</expan></choice> totoque orbe <choice><abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Celeberrimo</expan></choice> D. Johanni <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> Petrus Antonius <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotti</rs>.</salute></opener>
<p>Tandem ante quindecim dies mihi reddit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt a <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnato</rs>
<lb/>Tuo <rs key="B_991170515153305501" type="letter">Litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><!-- Prüfen: Es könnte sich um den Brief 000059217 vom 30.10.1717. handeln. -->, quas ad me misisti humanissimas doctrinales atque
             <lb/>eruditione plenas: pro quibus Tibi nunc maximas ago gratias
             <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ternumque referam. Tuis Doctrinis utar in mea <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">exercitatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ne</rs><!--Prüfen: Meint evtl. entweder Michelottis  X. Animadversiones (gegen Keill) oder noch seine ungedruckte Dissertation: Michelotti, Pietro Antonio, De separatione fluidorum in corpore animali dissertatio physico-mechanico-medica, Venetiis (A. &amp; A. Pinelli) 1721. (Digitalisat bei BSB digital). Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer. Getaggt ist vorläufig die Dissertation--> quam proximo mense Januarii pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>lo committi curabo.
             <lb/>Gratum mihi fecisti Vir Amicissime significando expensas
             <lb/>quas facere coactus fuisti in accipiendis meis litteris<!-- Es sind Michelottis Briefe im allgemeinen gemeint. Prüfen: Es muss sich um einen Brief von Michelotti an Joh. I B. handeln, der mit Beilagen für Nic. II B. --> cum <rs type="letter">an<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nexis</rs><!-- Prüfen: An Nic. II B. adressierte Beilage-Brief(e) zu einem Joh. I B.-Brief. --> ad <choice><abbr>ingeniosiss.<hi rend="sup">m</hi></abbr><expan>ingeniosissimum</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Fili<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiis</rs> commorant<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, ad quem spero
             <lb/>te meam ultim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> transmisisse <rs key="B_991170515153105501" type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Michelotti wünschte sich, dass sein Brief vom November 1717 durch Johann I an dessen Sohn Nikolaus II weitergeleitet werde.</note>. Ita constituo Vir
             <lb/><choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissime</expan></choice> (modo Tibi placeat) expensas, quas in accipiendis et
             <lb/>mittendis litteris ad me spectantibus persolvam eo quo
             <lb/>voles tempore <choice><abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Celeberrimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnato</rs> Tuo, qui cras de hac re, spero,
             <lb/>Te admonebit. Quatuor credo meas epistolas accepisti. Duos
             <lb/>ergo pro illis florenos dabo ipsi D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao</rs> Nepoti Tuo ac
             <lb/>dimidi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> floren<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> pro hac quam nunc do. Mihi cariores
             <lb/>sunt tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>m aur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> quare nihil Tibi cogitand<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
             <lb/>erit de expensis siquid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ego prompte omnia persolvam. Spe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rans ergo te hoc pactum me<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> non esse recusatur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> venio ad
             <lb/>aliquas qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stiones ad meam exercitation<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> pertinentes.</p>
<p>Harmoni<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> seu conspiration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> motuum <choice><sic>intenstinor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></sic><corr>intestinor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></corr></choice> consen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tienti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Tu et <choice><abbr>Illustriss.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118571249" type="person">Leibnitius</rs> adhibuistis pro reddenda
             <lb/>aliqua ratione cur Liquores cognatis adh<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>rescant, et cur
             <lb/>Humores animales potius in his qu<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>m illis Glandulis
             <lb/>a principio generationis similibus Liquoribus imbutis
             <lb/>colentur aut secernantur a communi mistaque Humor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
             <lb/>massa. Objiciet fortassis aliquis conspirationem
             <lb/>motuum intestinor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> parti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Liquores similes inte<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1078967" n="2"/><lb break="no"/>granti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Locum haud habere posse in canalibus arteriosis:
             <lb/>qui quum sint elastici et alternis, non minus qu<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>m Cor,
             <lb/>contractionibus ac dilatationibus Humores omnes mistim
             <lb/>fluentes per arterias ipsas, premant, urgeant atque
             <lb/>agitent, ideoque cogant eosdem fluere per suas cavi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tates duplici motu circulari scilicet seu lationis uno,
             <lb/>agitativo sive turbativo altero: contingat oportet ut
             <lb/>conspirationes motu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> suar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> partium perturben<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur aut aboleantur pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pollentibus motu circulari atque
             <lb/>agitativo. Hoc argumento utor ad convellendum <rs key="pers_DE-588-1055365613" type="person">Keillii</rs>
<lb/>sistema. Hic enim auctor attractionibus partium
             <lb/>Humores constituenti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Liquores in arteriis ipsis gene<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rari ac coagmentari credit<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>;</reg></choice> quo posito infert eos Li<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quores quorum partes viribus attra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>hentibus fortissimis gaudent separari in minima a cor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>de distantia et huius generis censet esse Liquor<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> Capsu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Cordis sive Pericardii, Lympham etc. quorum ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>
             <lb/>partes viribus attrahentibus debilibus sunt refert<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
             <lb/>uniuntur in maxima a Corde distantia id est ubi mi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nima est sanguinis circulantis vis, minimaque par<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> agitatio<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>;</reg></choice> et huiusmodi esse arbitratur partes Li<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quorem mucilaginos<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> qui in Glandulis mucilaginosis
             <lb/>articulor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> separatur. Rogo itaque ut cogites an San<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>guinis motus circularis et agitativus, vald<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> officere
             <lb/>possit conspirationi motu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> intestinor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, per quos
             <lb/>credo Te intelligere eos motus qui a nulla causa
             <pb facs="1078968" n="3"/>
<lb/>externa impellente excitantur; sed a gravitatibus
             <lb/>parti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> specificis, earundem elatere aliisque viri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus iisdem partibus insitis<choice><sic>.</sic><corr type="deleted"/></choice> pendent. Fermentatio sane,
             <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> est motus parti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> intestinus, a maxima Medico<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>r<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> parte in statu saltem naturali sanguini dene<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gatur propterea qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> sanguinis partes a Viribus cordis
             <lb/>atque arteriar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> propuls<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in suis intimis motioni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus turbari rationi consentane<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> videtur. Res est
             <lb/>non exigui momenti quare ut cogitationes tuas mi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>hi communices etiam atque etiam rogo. Res huc redit.
             <lb/>Fluido mixto ex pluribus Liquoribus propulso a
             <lb/>quibuscunque Viribus continuo agentibus per canali<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
             <lb/>altern<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> sese contrahenti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> et dilatanti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> sectiones cer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ta celeritate fluente<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ritur num motum aliquem intes<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tin<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> suar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> parti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> pendent<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> a specificis parti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
             <lb/>affectionibus viribusque insitis habere et conserva<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re possit. Statim aut quamprim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> fieri poterit respon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>s<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> super hac re a Te expecto.</p> <closer><salute>Interim Vale Vir
                <lb/><choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissime</expan></choice> mihi que favere perge.</salute>
<dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice>
<lb/><date when="1717-11-12">12 Novembris 1717</date>.</dateline></closer>
<postscript><p>P. S. Salutem plurim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> meo nomine dicito jucundissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo et <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filio</rs> Tuo.</p></postscript>
